content:
(maartthommaa) pandithavydyaa!-rogaarttharkkaayu
saukhyamiyattituvaanadhikaaram the nalki paran
paartthaal ninna sthikalathre njangalkkabhayam;
njangate yaachana nin praarththanayaal nal-keetatte;
/taarogyam vyaadhigrastharkkum
/tvishraamam-peeditha janathaykkum;
kshama njangalkkum prathyaagamanam doorastharkkum.
